","msg":"已被色誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50565b1a7c5a14e0f8bba7012a5e07842385b44","tid":2160693,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40fecec6ee1217ca0128befa5a62042afc7ff52","tid":2160693,"uid":222970,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/東京玫瑰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E7%8E%AB%E7%91%B0&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=75955f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/東京玫瑰</a><br />\n<br />\n東京玫瑰是二次大戰時，美軍對東京廣播電台（今NHK）的女播音員的暱稱。<br />\n<br />\n當時日軍企圖以廣播進行心理戰，利用女播音員對太平洋上的美軍發送英語廣播，企圖勾起美軍的鄉愁和厭戰情緒。<br />\n<br />\n在戰爭結束後美國的調查中發現，當時負責廣播的女性播音員可能有4至20位，但僅有一名日裔美國人戶栗郁子承認了自己的身分。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"四面楚歌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fe8f0e54ea8eeb07f8d4af576de2e89029bb39","tid":2160693,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"T.Lok@TszLok18<br />\n<br />\n12 小時回覆給 <br />\n@SolomonYue 和 @ledzepfan400<br />\nI wonder if Angela Merkel is one of them<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d01ef44d973db903bd0405ea18a1482deb07b","tid":2160693,"uid":251660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T22:00:21.000Z","msg":"勁撚多垃圾撐呢條八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6eb341461a237cc2b8e88ed6450cf6aaf2e8aa4","tid":2160693,"uid":120499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"Pish <br />\n<br />\n已經證實呢個德國臭閪係同一個支那人結咗婚，佢有解放軍背景，德國人真係罪無可恕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif